  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This integrated research project is cooperated by an fully-experienced team of Taipei Medical
      University and National Institutes of Health. We hope that we can find out the disease of
      balance, anxiety and sick headaches through the translation of basic research to clinical
      diagnosis and treatment of Mild Traumatic Brain Injury (mTBI).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
